<template>
  <EasyDataTable
    :headers="headers"
    :items="items"
  />
</template>
<script>
import type { Header, Item } from "vue3-easy-data-table";
export default defineComponent({
  setup() {
    const headers: Header[] = [
      { text: "Name 1", value: "name 1" },
      // ...
    ];
    const items: Item[] = [
      { "name": "Item 1", "height": 178, "weight": 77, "age": 20 },
      // ...
    ];
    return {
      headers,
      items
    };
  },
});
</script>
